## Consequences

- All capabilities are written in {{stack.language}} on {{stack.runtime}}.
- HTTP surface uses {{stack.api_framework}}.
- Persistent storage is {{stack.database}}; cross-store consistency requires explicit ADRs.
- UI is built on {{stack.ui_framework}}; deployment is {{stack.deployment_target}}.
- Quality gates: `{{quality_gates.lint}}`, `{{quality_gates.format}}`, `{{quality_gates.type_check}}`, `{{quality_gates.test}}` are mandatory before merge.

